            <title>[SOLR-2327] java.lang.ArithmeticException: / by zero with queryResultCache size=0 and queryResultWindowSize=0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2327</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
